{"tid":1205675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新白宮聯署] 對違反美國利益的香港官員實施制裁","createTime":"2019-06-11T22:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T10:39:51.000Z","uid":213167,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6db93db811f841fff39bcc66fe052b33b7fb8b6a","tid":1205675,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:14:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">對違反美國利益的香港官員實施制裁 <br />\nImpose sanctions upon Hong Kong officials who are acting against American interests.<br />\n</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港政府即將通過引渡法案。 如果成功，前往香港的美國公民將面臨因無限期過去發生的罪行而被引渡到中國大陸的風險，或中國政府為推進其政治利益而製造的&ldquo;罪行&rdquo;。 鑑於正在進行的貿易戰和過去中國特工綁架外國公民，美國在那裡面臨的利益所面臨的風險既有形也有不可接受。 我們請求美國政府對推動這項法案的香港政客以及與美國有著密切聯繫的美國居民實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong government is on the verge of passing an extradition bill. If succeeds, US citizens traveling to Hong Kong would be at risk of being extradited to the Mainland China for crimes occurred there from the indefinite past, or &lsquo;crimes&rsquo; fabricated by the PRC government to advance its political interests. In light of the ongoing trade war and past abductions of foreign citizens by Chinese agents, the risk facing US interests there is both tangible and unacceptable. We petition for the US Government to impose a sanction against the Hong Kong politicians who push for these bills, and any individuals residing in the US with known ties to them.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/impose-sanctions-upon-hong-kong-officials-who-are-acting-against-american-interests?fbclid=IwAR3DG8V4B7KHxUr3KItrwItIt6FwhmZiT5T1gGN9d4XFYMPuWAvJvg78pAk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fimpose-sanctions-upon-hong-kong-officials-who-are-acting-against-american-interests%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3DG8V4B7KHxUr3KItrwItIt6FwhmZiT5T1gGN9d4XFYMPuWAvJvg78pAk&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvn0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=be41a673\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/impose-sanctions-upon-hong-kong-officials-who-are-acting-against-american-interests?fbclid=IwAR3DG8V4B7KHxUr3KItrwItIt6FwhmZiT5T1gGN9d4XFYMPuWAvJvg78pAk</a>"},{"pid":"301847c471b3605adc3b7bc79c457fc929502806","tid":1205675,"uid":201015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:16:57.000Z","msg":"已簽 push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34787519523839918383788bf7e461946fe13878","tid":1205675,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:18:15.000Z","msg":"done"},{"pid":"66fb089a5b0fed521bead8dd6bb5dd9ebc403313","tid":1205675,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261ceb264e99833b59e699451cc7b6c9a229a66a","tid":1205675,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:21:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfff3c71090da2dfb921b33fb093bd556d03a5e0","tid":1205675,"uid":19557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:22:07.000Z","msg":"我覺得直接send 去侵侵twitter 實質d 上次果個仲未有回音"},{"pid":"78babb4527ce85f1c031038aa73fd3408420c0e7","tid":1205675,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:22:58.000Z","msg":"signed"},{"pid":"46c86a1e5602c05b746e312fd4daebdf39d1a0fa","tid":1205675,"uid":40688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:24:22.000Z","msg":"已簽"},{"pid":"010eadbd89537d85b73a9043917cbd01a229a892","tid":1205675,"uid":42155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:26:09.000Z","msg":"落實香港人權問責法"},{"pid":"e0e7cee33c7dd968f66bb4e26155767ab106ce85","tid":1205675,"uid":77759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:33:40.000Z","msg":"Done<img src=\"/assets/face